1
00:00:47,680 --> 00:00:49,680
Ling'er, what happened exactly?

2
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:52,680
Diyun, do you know the art of puppetry?

3
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,920
Of course I do. Why?

4
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,760
I need you to make a puppet of me

5
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:57,820
to go back with you.

6
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,680
Ling'er, what are you planning?

7
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,240
The Demon Lord set a trap.

8
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:03,360
He took on the appearance of my father,

9
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,760
making me witness Yunyuan killing him.

10
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:08,520
I need you to take a copy of me back with you.

11
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:10,810
I have more important things to do.

12
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:11,640
No.

13
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,000
It's too dangerous.

14
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:13,730
Don't worry.

15
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:16,610
I have restored my true form and spiritual power.

16
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,010
Ling'er.

17
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:23,600
You really did it.

18
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,200
I did it.

19
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:28,400
Since the Demon Lord set a trap,

20
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,160
we might as well play along.

21
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:39,759
Okay.

22
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,479
Not bad.

23
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,240
Thank you.

24
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:58,240
There is no need for thanks between us.

25
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,360
Ling'er.

26
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,640
I've already hidden my aura.

27
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,360
How did you still find me?

28
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,720
How is your injury?

29
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,640
Let me see.

30
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:21,810
Look, Princess.

31
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,240
It hurts.

32
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:29,000
Don't you know how to dodge?

33
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,880
You just keep getting yourself hurt.

34
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:33,040
You are not allowed to do this again. This body is mine.

35
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:33,960
Do you hear me?

36
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:35,960
I hear you.

37
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:39,560
My body belongs to Your Highness.

38
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,960
Be serious.

39
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,440
To save me,

40
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,480
you...

41
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:50,680
Ling'er.

42
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:54,079
Now that Your Highness has restored your true form,

43
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,120
from now on,

44
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:58,240
I can hide safely behind Your Highness

45
00:02:58,480 --> 00:03:00,410
and be your little dragon husband.

46
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,280
Shameless.

47
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,000
But what?

48
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:08,860
It's not impossible if you want to be my little dragon husband.

49
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,160
Princess.

50
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,040
Keep pretending.

51
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,340
I'm here to talk about serious business.

52
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,360
Ao Ling, get out here!

53
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,200
You feathered beast,

54
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,680
why are you wailing so early in the morning?

55
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,200
Damn.

56
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,060
Calling me a feathered beast?

57
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,420
I'll endure it.

58
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:41,360
Where is Ao Ling? Tell her to get out here!

59
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,560
Sister Qingluan,

60
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,370
why are you here?

61
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,920
Don't call me sister. You don't deserve it.

62
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:54,900
Miss Qingluan,

63
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,440
please look clearly.

64
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,960
This is my residence,

65
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,520
and I won't tolerate your insolence.

66
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,050
Exactly.

67
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,960
Open your bird eyes and see where this is.

68
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:05,080
Did King Kunmi forget to leash you?

69
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,360
How did you get out?

70
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:08,330
Your master hasn't barked yet,

71
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,680
but you're already yapping.

72
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,120
You...

73
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,440
My Lord.

74
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:12,840
Ao Ling,

75
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:15,130
my sworn brother treated you well,

76
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,440
but you actually tried to kill him.

77
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,240
Today,

78
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:22,079
I will drag you to my brother's grave to kowtow and apologize.

79
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,520
He killed my father.

80
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,060
Meeting such an end

81
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,280
is his retribution.

82
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,920
My sworn brother is barely cold in his grave,

83
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:35,680
yet you've already thrown yourself into another's arms.

84
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:38,640
My sworn brother trusted the wrong person.

85
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,080
Diyun and I have always been betrothed.

86
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:43,480
Do not slander my good name with empty words.

87
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,680
Enough nonsense.

88
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,480
You changed the plan.

89
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,640
Why wasn't I informed?

90
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,720
The plan did change.

91
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,920
I'm taking Ling'er with me.

92
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,280
What?

93
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,930
You're taking Ling'er?

94
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,120
My Lord, are you alright?

95
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,720
That was a heavy blow.

96
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:14,580
My Lord.

97
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,480
Are you okay?

98
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,360
I'm fine.

99
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,880
Diyun, where is Ling'er?

100
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,760
Qingluan? Weren't you...

101
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,600
Weren't I what? Where is Ling'er?

102
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,440
My sworn brother is critically injured and hanging by a thread.

103
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,440
Bring Ling'er out, quickly.

104
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:28,280
Come with me to see him one last time.

105
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,280
Who exactly are you?

106
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,520
I am Qingluan.

107
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:32,700
This is bad.

108
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:35,680
Someone impersonating you just took the Ling'er I created.

109
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:38,159
The fake Ling'er was taken by the fake me.

110
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,820
Then this plan won't work.

111
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,120
Let's regroup with your sworn brother first.

112
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:42,920
Okay.

113
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,560
Didn't you want me to kowtow?

114
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,840
Princess of the Dragon Clan.

115
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:57,000
If you hand over the Seven-Colored Divine Stone,

116
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,760
I will spare your life.

117
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,840
Otherwise...

118
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,000
Whether I hand it over or not,

119
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,090
you're going to kill me anyway.

120
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,320
That's true.

121
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,280
My apologies.

122
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:10,080
I say that every time I see you.

123
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,960
It's become a habit.

124
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,320
If you knew it would end like this,

125
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:23,380
why did you bother in the first place?

126
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,240
Why aren't you bleeding?

127
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,440
Li Sha.

128
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:34,760
My Lord.

129
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,420
Did you get the Seven-Colored Stone?

130
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,040
Spare me, My Lord.

131
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,640
I failed in my duty.

132
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:43,820
I was deceived by their puppetry.

133
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:44,640
Humph.

134
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,000
You are incapable of success,

135
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,600
yet more than capable of failure.

136
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,860
Spare my life, My Lord!

137
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:44,530
Let my Heart-Protecting Scale become the mirror on your armor.

138
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,200
To keep you safe,

139
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,980
and help you triumph in every battle.

140
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:01,160
Girl, I do not wish to hurt you.

141
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,880
Just hand over the Seven-Colored Stone,

142
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:06,680
and I will let you live.

143
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,480
My dear daughter.

144
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:21,760
Give the Seven-Colored Stone to Father.

145
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,400
Ling'er, look out!

146
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,840
He is not your father!

147
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,500
Demon Lord!

148
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,500
Your eye sorcery won't work on me.

149
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,080
Father!

150
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,340
How can this be?

151
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,679
My Ling'er.

152
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,340
It's so good...

153
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,120
that you finally woke up.

154
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,520
Watch out!

155
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,640
Yunyuan.

156
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,840
Yunyuan.

157
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,640
Yunyuan.

158
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,920
Ling'er.

159
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,560
I'm sorry.

160
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,680
I can no longer

161
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,640
protect you.

162
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:17,480
Yunyuan.

163
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,160
Ling'er.

164
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:22,920
You must...

165
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:24,320
I know.

166
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,600
I know. Don't speak.

167
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,530
Yunyuan.

168
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,360
Yunyuan.

169
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,120
Yunyuan.

170
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,840
Don't leave me.

171
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:47,320
Yunyuan, don't leave me behind.

172
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,000
Demon Lord.

173
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,640
If killing is your nature,

174
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,760
then today I will end violence with violence

175
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,820
to comfort the myriad souls of Kunmi.

176
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,600
My Ling'er.

177
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:24,900
How can this be?

178
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,800
I...

179
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:28,120
...finally see you safe and sound.

180
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,280
My Ling'er.

181
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,240
You've suffered all these years.

182
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,050
My little princess.

183
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,120
Father.

184
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:39,720
Father.

185
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,640
Father.

186
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,600
I, the Dragon Lord,

187
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:47,200
was controlled by the Demon Tribe for thousands of years.

188
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:49,360
I have truly failed my ancestors.

189
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:52,000
To perish together with Ye Yin,

190
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:54,880
I die with no regrets.

191
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,640
Father.

192
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,920
This isn't true, Father.

193
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:58,840
Ling'er.

194
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,730
Ten thousand years ago,

195
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:04,120
Ye Yin died at the hands of the Heavenly Emperor and me.

196
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:05,500
Unexpectedly,

197
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:09,520
relying on his extraordinary soul power,

198
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:12,050
he cultivated the Demonic Spirit Art.

199
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:15,120
He entered my body while I was critically injured,

200
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:18,160
and forced my Inner Core

201
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,600
to merge with his.

202
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:23,920
Now that I end my own life,

203
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:26,040
he cannot live either.

204
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,280
My Ling'er.

205
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,760
You must live on well.

206
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,720
Father!

207
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,640
With just your soul power,

208
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,560
you think you can destroy me?

209
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:43,400
You overestimate yourself.

210
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:48,320
Ye Yin, die!

211
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:52,600
Dragon Lord, you are too naive.

212
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,920
You overestimate yourself.

213
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:06,080
Actually, your father's body

214
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:07,770
wasn't very useful.

215
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,760
A young body...

216
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,060
What are you doing?

217
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,080
Stay back.

218
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,540
Don't even think about it.

219
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:19,560
You killed my father and my husband.

220
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:21,200
You killed the people of Kunmi.

221
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,660
Even if my body and soul are destroyed today,

222
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:26,010
I won't let you desecrate Yunyuan's body.

223
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:33,040
Ancient Seal!

224
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:34,800
How do you know...

225
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:43,040
How dare you hurt me like this!

226
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,800
I will make this Kunmi

227
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,720
be buried with me!

228
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,640
My Lord.

229
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:51,840
General.

230
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:57,600
Oh no.

231
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,520
The Kunmi Earth Ruins seal an endless fire.

232
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,320
Stop him!

233
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:07,000
Soldiers of the Demon Tribe, listen to my order.

234
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,860
Help His Majesty open the Earth Veins immediately!

235
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,680
The Endless Flame is the fire of ancient wars.

236
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:17,540
If the seal breaks, Kunmi will become a living hell.

237
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,880
This is the Kunmi my Yun Yuan guarded for a thousand years.

238
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:32,480
You cannot destroy it just because you wish to.

239
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,000
Di Yun.

240
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,700
Take care of him for me.

241
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:39,730
Ling'er.

242
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:40,980
What are you doing?

243
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,650
I leave Kunmi in your hands.

244
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:45,400
Ling'er.

245
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:46,650
Princess. Ling'er.

246
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:50,280
What is she doing?

247
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,640
With my soul,

248
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,400
I enter your spirit

249
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,520
to protect my people

250
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:00,520
and bless the world.

251
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:04,140
Oh no. The Princess is sacrificing herself.

252
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:06,640
Yun Yuan.

253
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:10,600
This is the Kunmi you guarded for a thousand years.

254
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,280
I will protect it for you.

255
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,560
With my spirit,

256
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,280
I offer my soul.

257
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,960
With my body as the formation,

258
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:38,000
I shall destroy evil.

259
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,040
Ling'er.

260
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,600
General.

261
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:48,640
You two...

262
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,720
are together now, in a different way.

263
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,280
Ling'er.

264
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:05,920
The Kunmi that you and Yun Yuan always protected,

265
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:09,000
I will guard it from now on.

266
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:25,800
Recruitment.
